name: Woices
tag_list: audio, lbs, gps, map, geo-tag, mashup, community, voice, mobile-phone
overview: Woices, World voices, is an Internet start-up company founded in 2007 that provides Location Based Audio Services (LBS). It offers a free basic service, already available at http://woices.com, which allows its users to create, manage and play echos: audio records associated to a precise real-world location or object, such as audio guides. Woices ultimate goal is to create the largest worldwide layer of user contributed oral information, that we call the echosphere, and make the world a more interesting place.
